window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The hunters have become the hunted. </p> <p>Outnumbered, outsmarted, and desperate, the hunters are on the run, pursued by the vampaneze, the police, and an angry mob. With their enemies clamoring for blood, the vampires prepare for a deadly battle. Is this the end for Darren and his allies? </p> <p>This third and final installment in the Hunters trilogy finds Darren and his friends facing their longest night and most testing challenge yet. </p>"; 
